<TEXT>
<P>
The June 3 TV Times cover on the nightmarish "Tales From the Crypt" turned into 
a parent's nightmare, or should I say children's nightmare. 
</P>
<P>
I guess I could have ripped the cover page off our TV Times or try to hide it. 
</P>
<P>
I guess what I'm saying is I'd just wish a slightly less scarier picture had 
been used so our entire family, which includes my 4-year-old son, could have 
enjoyed it. I also have an 8-year-old and we often peruse TV Times together to 
encourage reading. 
</P>
<P>
Margie Simmers, Manhattan Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
