<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE MIND'S EYE: WHY THE RECKLESS SURVIVE . . . AND OTHER SECRETS OF HUMAN 
NATURE BY MELVIN KONNER (VIKING: $18.95; 288 PP.) 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ALEX RAKSIN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TYPE>
<P>
Book Review; Column 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA062490-0010 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 237822 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
