<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB; 
</P>
<P>
MAN VS. MICROCHIP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Once again, I had two-thirds of a triple bet, losing $18 Saturday. My bets for 
