runs. 
</P>
<P>
Neely and Horcher, a 38-year-old attorney, are stressing their conservative 
credentials. Manning disagrees. "From my perspective, we have two candidates 
who are moderates. The conservatives don't have anybody to vote for," he said. 
</P>
<P>
