square feet; $449,500-$465,000; builder, Hix Development; August move-ins; open 
10 a.m.-6 p.m. daily at 128 Worthy Drive, near Loraine Avenue, reached from 
northbound Grand Avenue exit of the Foothill (210) Freeway. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
San Bernardino Co. 
</P>
<P>
ONTARIO: Phase 1 of Watt Homes at Archibald, 19 of 120 3-5-bedroom 
single-family houses; 1,801-2,559 square feet; $190,900-$239,900; builder, Watt 
Homes Inland Empire; August move-ins; open 10 a.m.-6 p.m. daily at 2967 Golden 
Trails St., reached from the northbound Archibald Avenue exit of the San 
Bernardino (10) Freeway. 
</P>
