<P>
Photo, Kirk Gibson has struggled since leading Dodgers to World Series victory 
over A's in 1988. ; Photo, COLOR, (Orange County Edition) Kirk Gibson has 
struggled since leading Dodgers to World Series victory over A's in 1988. LORI 
SHEPLER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
