performs with other troupe members in San Antonio. TOMMY HULTGREN; Photo, 
Kichiemon mingles with the locals in a country bar at Hondo, outside San 
Antonio. ; Photo, Sawkamura Sojura IX portrays a philandering husband in the 
Grand Kabuki Theatre's "Migawari Zazen" 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
